'''Zinsian''' was a dry preservative.<ref name="Alliance Intelligence Reports">''[[Alliance Intelligence Reports]]''</ref>

==Overview==
A vein of Zinsian was discovered on the planet [[Brosi]], in the [[Corporate Sector/Legends|Corporate Sector]]. The [[Corporate Sector Authority/Legends|Corporate Sector Authority]] decided to build three Zinsian processing plants ([[Delta 1]], [[Delta 2]] and [[Mailor]]). To do so, they displaced thousands of native Brosins, and many young male Brosins were "hired" by supervisors to work in dangerous extractions. The Brosins then created the [[Brosin Underground]] to fight this industrial activity.<ref name="Alliance Intelligence Reports" />

